---

## Overview

BitTheWriteup is a lightweight Python utility that automatically collects high-quality Bug Bounty writeups from trusted security research sources and sends them directly to a Discord channel using a webhook.

---

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/0xdragon/bitthewriteup.git
cd bitthewriteup

cp config.example.json config.json
```

Python **3.9+** required. No external dependencies.

---

## Configuration

Edit `config.json` and set your Discord webhook:

```json
{
  "discord_webhook": "https://discord.com/api/webhooks/YOUR_WEBHOOK"
}
```

Create a Discord webhook:

```
Discord
└── Channel Settings
    └── Integrations
        └── Webhooks
            └── New Webhook
```

---

## Usage

```bash
python3 bitthewriteup.py --dry-run
python3 bitthewriteup.py
python3 bitthewriteup.py --once
python3 bitthewriteup.py --refresh
python3 bitthewriteup.py --summary
python3 bitthewriteup.py --status
python3 bitthewriteup.py --list
```

